msgid "# Clear-HgsServer"
msgstr "# Clear-HgsServer"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概要"

msgid ""
"Resets the Host Guardian Service on the local node to the uninitialized "
"state."
msgstr "将本地节点上的Host Guardian服务重置为未初始化的状态。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 描述"

msgid ""
"The **Clear-HgsServer** cmdlet removes a local node from the Host Guardian "
"Service (HGS)."
msgstr "`Clear-HgsServer` 这个 cmdlet 用于将本地节点从 Host Guardian Service (HGS) 中删除。"

msgid ""
"This cmdlet makes the following infrastructure component changes on the "
"additional HGS node:"
msgstr "此cmdlet会在额外的HGS节点上执行以下基础设施组件更改："

msgid ""
"For more information about the scenario terms, see [Security and "
"Assurance](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=699209)."
msgstr ""
"有关场景术语的更多信息，请参阅[安全性和保障措施](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=699209)。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid ""
"### Example 1: Clear all cluster initialization settings from the local node"
msgstr "### 示例 1：清除本地节点上的所有集群初始化设置"

msgid ""
"This command returns the HGS Server on the local node to a clean state to "
"prepare it for the **Initialize-HgsServer** command."
msgstr ""
"此命令会将本地节点上的HGS服务器恢复到初始状态（即“干净”状态），以便为其后续执行**Initialize-HgsServer**命令做好准备。"

msgid ""
"### Example 2: Clear all cluster initialization settings from the local node"
" without confirmation"
msgstr "### 示例 2：在未经确认的情况下，清除本地节点上的所有集群初始化设置"

msgid ""
"This command returns the HGS Server on the local node to a clean state to "
"prepare it for the **Initialize-HgsServer** command and does not prompt for "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"该命令会将本地节点上的HGS服务器恢复到初始状态（即“干净”状态），以便后续执行**Initialize-"
"HgsServer**命令。在执行此命令时，系统不会要求用户进行确认。"

msgid "## PARAMETERS"
msgstr "## 参数"

msgid "Specifies a cluster name."
msgstr "指定一个集群名称。"

msgid "Forces the command to run without asking for user confirmation."
msgstr "强制命令执行，而不会询问用户的确认。"

msgid "Prompts you for confirmation before running the cmdlet."
msgstr "在运行该 cmdlet 之前，会提示您进行确认。"

msgid ""
"Shows what would happen if the cmdlet runs.\n"
"The cmdlet is not run."
msgstr "展示了如果运行该cmdlet会发生什么情况。但实际上并没有运行这个cmdlet。"

